  <mads:note type="source">Basil I. Ammaestramenti dell&amp;#039;imperadore Basilio a suo
      figliuolo Leone il Filosofo, 1796</mads:note>
  <mads:note type="source">Papyros Larous (Leo&#x304;n 6., ho Sophos, Emperor of the Byzantium, 886-912;
      attributed to him is the Eparchiakon vivlion)</mads:note>
  <mads:note type="source">Hoi histore&#x304;menoi chre&#x304;smoi tou Leontos 6. tou Sophou, 1995: p. 276
      (Leone il Saggio; Leone VI il Saggio (886-912))</mads:note>
  <mads:note type="source">Autokratoros Leontos, taktika, 2001: t.p. (Ho autokrato&#x304;r Leo&#x304;n VI, ho
      Sophos)</mads:note>
